OL,6,FThe BBC's Wimbledon coverage saw the  
OL,7,Fintroduction of a new BBC Sport       
OL,8,Fgraphics package. I began to recreate 
OL,9,Fthe on-screen graphics, firstly as    
OL,10,Fstills, but with the aim of eventually
OL,11,Frecreating the animations.            
OL,13,FAs a 'what if' I applied the graphics 
OL,14,Fto the BBC's coverage of the Winter   
OL,15,FOlympic Games.                        
OL,17,FWhen the BBC updated the graphics used
OL,18,Ffor Final Score, they kept the previous
OL,19,Flayout and simply updated the design  
OL,20,Fand animations to match the new BBC   
OL,21,FSport branding.                       
OL,3,CBBC Sport on-screen graphics recreated
OL,4,Cand updated                           
OL,22,                                   G1/3
