OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F346A1662210293
OL,6,FMy animated recreation of the name    
OL,7,Fstrap is largely the same as the      
OL,8,Fversion we've seen used for Wimbledon 
OL,9,Fand the Commonwealth Games. This      
OL,10,Fversion has the yellow (and multicolour
OL,11,Fgradient) portion of the strap fade   
OL,12,Finto place. I prefer this to other    
OL,13,Fversions which use a vertical stretch 
OL,14,Finstead.                              
OL,16,FThe only element of the original      
OL,17,Fgraphic I changed is the animation of 
OL,18,Fthe BBC Sport logo. The fade version  
OL,19,Fmoved a bit too quickly, so I swapped 
OL,20,Fit for the slower version used on the 
OL,21,Fstretch animation.                    
